  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nThe current release contains a remote signer implementation, and internal libs to consume the remote signer endpoint, however, it appears that the only validator_definition supported is that of LocalKeystore - and that Lighthose cannot currently be configured to consume a Remote signer endpoint.\r\n\r\n ## Version\r\nLighthouse v1.4.0/stable\r\nRust v1.5.0\r\n\r\n## Present Behaviour\r\n\r\nLocalKeystore is hardcoded as the only validator_definition supported\r\n\r\n## Expected Behaviour\r\n\r\nRemoteKeystore should be configurable from the command line interface\r\n\r\n## Steps to resolve\r\n\r\nImplement logic integrating remote_signer_consumer and add RemoteSigner validator_definition.\r\n",
